text: Zakia Tabassum is a Bangladeshi politician who was elected as Member of 11th Jatiya Sangsad of Reserved Seats for Women. She is a politician of Bangladesh Awami League. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Awami League politicians Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Women members of the Jatiya Sangsad Category:People from Dinajpur District, Bangladesh Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
